title: Otis Redding &ndash; The Platinum Collection (Flac) [FrankFoo]
description:
Otis Redding - The Platinum Collection (2007) (MP3@320)

Info:
2007 import compilation from the late, great '60s Soul belter. 
While Otis Redding died in 1967, just as he was achieving the success he so richly deserved, his recorded output proves that his talents were in full force even before the world began to take notice. 
No man before or since could sing Soul music with as much passion as Otis. 
This release collects some of the best of his Atlantic recordings including 'Sittin' On The Dock Of The Bay', 'Try A Little Tenderness', 'Hard To Handle' and 'I Can't Turn You Loose'. 16 tracks and every one of them is a winner. 


Included: NFO, PLS, M3U
